### AI 积分系统 API 测试
### 使用 VS Code REST Client 插件运行

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ==================== 用户认证 ====================

### 1. 注册新用户（会自动获得 50000 积分）
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试用户",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. 登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### ==================== 积分管理 ====================

### 3. 获取用户余额
GET {{baseUrl}}/credit/balance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 获取使用统计（最近7天）
GET {{baseUrl}}/credit/usage-stats?days=7
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 获取充值套餐
GET {{baseUrl}}/credit/plans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. 创建充值订单（充值 50 元）
POST {{baseUrl}}/credit/recharge
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50,
  "paymentMethod": "wechat"
}

### 7. 模拟支付回调（测试用，实际生产环境需要验证签名）
POST {{baseUrl}}/credit/payment-callback
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderNo": "YOUR_ORDER_NO_HERE",
  "paymentId": "wx_payment_123456"
}

### 8. 升级到 Pro 会员
POST {{baseUrl}}/credit/upgrade-tier
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tier": "pro"
}

### ==================== AI 服务 ====================

### 9. 获取可用模型列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/ai/models
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. AI 对话 - GPT-4o Mini（免费用户可用）
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "openai",
  "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "你好，请用一句话介绍你自己"
    }
  ],
  "temperature": 0.7,
  "maxTokens": 100
}

### 11. AI 对话 - Claude 3.5 Haiku（免费用户可用）
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "anthropic",
  "model": "claude-3-5-haiku-20241022",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "解释一下什么是量子计算"
    }
  ],
  "temperature": 0.7,
  "maxTokens": 200
}

### 12. AI 对话 - 豆包 Pro（免费用户可用）
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "doubao",
  "model": "doubao-pro-32k",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "帮我写一首关于春天的诗"
    }
  ],
  "temperature": 0.9,
  "maxTokens": 300
}

### 13. AI 对话 - GPT-4o（需要 Pro 会员）
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "openai",
  "model": "gpt-4o",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "分析一下 2024 年人工智能的发展趋势"
    }
  ],
  "temperature": 0.7,
  "maxTokens": 500
}

### 14. AI 对话 - 带工作流信息
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "openai",
  "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "帮我生成一个产品介绍"
    }
  ],
  "workflowId": "workflow_abc123",
  "executionId": "execution_def456",
  "temperature": 0.8,
  "maxTokens": 400
}

### 15. 测试 AI 连接
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/test-connection
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "openai"
}

### ==================== 工作流测试 ====================

### 16. 多轮对话示例
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "openai",
  "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "我想开一家咖啡店"
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "开咖啡店是个不错的想法！需要考虑选址、装修、设备采购等..."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "帮我列一个启动资金预算清单"
    }
  ],
  "temperature": 0.7,
  "maxTokens": 600
}

### ==================== 错误测试 ====================

### 17. 测试积分不足（将 maxTokens 设得很大）
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "openai",
  "model": "gpt-4o",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "写一篇10000字的论文"
    }
  ],
  "maxTokens": 10000
}

### 18. 测试等级限制（免费用户调用高级模型）
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "anthropic",
  "model": "claude-3-opus-20240229",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "测试"
    }
  ]
}

### ==================== 管理接口 ====================

### 19. 获取用户资料（含会员等级）
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
